o years, three years, two years before she died, I have seen her - we used to have the - old fashioned grates, do you remember, like the bars, I've seen my mother - down there - polishing. You know, the top part, used to be the black. I've seen my mother 
with a brush in her hand polishing. But as regards the making of fire, never used to see her make the fire.
